== 製作 ==
原著小說發行後不久，{{le|薩沃伊影業|Savoy Pictures}}以250萬美元的價格最先買下版權<ref>{{cite web |last1=Fleming Jr. |first1=Mike |title=Paramount Confirms Christopher McQuarrie Taking On Tom Clancy's 'Without Remorse' |url=https://deadline.com/2012/08/paramount-confirms-chrisopher-mcquarrie-taking-on-tom-clancys-without-remorse-314194/ |website=Deadline Hollywood |access-date=2018-07-12 |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309201333/https://deadline.com/2012/08/paramount-confirms-chrisopher-mcquarrie-taking-on-tom-clancys-without-remorse-314194/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之後以700萬美元聘請[[基努·李維|基努·李維]]飾演{{le|約翰·克拉克 (湯姆·克蘭西角色)|John Clark (Tom Clancy character)|約翰·克拉克}}，但遭到拒絕<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ew.com/article/1994/08/19/harrison-ford-takes-tom-clancyagain/|title=Harrison Ford takes on Tom Clancy...again|last1=Fretts|first1=Bruce|website=Entertainment Weekly|access-date=2018-09-22|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309040718/https://ew.com/article/1994/08/19/harrison-ford-takes-tom-clancyagain/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。儘管該片未能趕上預期1995年12月的發行日，但在與原著的作者[[湯姆·克蘭西|湯姆·克蘭西]]密切協商下，[[約翰·米利爾斯|約翰·米利爾斯]]加入擔任編導，使發展加快腳步<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://variety.com/1995/more/news/clancy-milius-military-minds-without-remorse-99129875/|title=Clancy, Milius: military minds ‘Without Remorse’|date=1995-08-07|website=Variety|language=en|access-date=2020-03-16|archive-date=2014-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141204033731/http://variety.com/1995/more/news/clancy-milius-military-minds-without-remorse-99129875/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》雜誌報導說[[勞倫斯·費許朋|勞倫斯·費許朋]]和[[蓋瑞·辛尼茲|蓋瑞·辛尼茲]]有望擔任主演；但因劇本問題和製片商的財務問題，製作被取消<ref>{{cite web |last1=Busch |first1=Anita M. |title=SAVOY WITHOUT 'REMORSE' |url=https://variety.com/1995/scene/markets-festivals/savoy-without-remorse-99129181/ |website=Variety |access-date=2018-09-22 |archive-date=2018-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180914094359/https://variety.com/1995/scene/markets-festivals/savoy-without-remorse-99129181/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。電影經歷數年[[開發地獄|開發地獄]]，直到[[克里斯多福·麥奎里|克里斯多福·麥奎里]]在2012年與[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙影業]]簽約執導<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2012/08/paramount-confirms-chrisopher-mcquarrie-taking-on-tom-clancys-without-remorse-314194/|title=Paramount Confirms Christopher McQuarrie Taking On Tom Clancy's 'Without Remorse'|first1=Mike Fleming|last1=Jr.|date=2012-08-07|access-date=2021-03-14|archive-date=2021-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316071244/https://deadline.com/2012/08/paramount-confirms-chrisopher-mcquarrie-taking-on-tom-clancys-without-remorse-314194/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。派拉蒙接洽[[湯姆·哈迪|湯姆·哈迪]]扮演克拉克，[[凱文·科斯納|凱文·科斯納]]有望回歸《[[傑克萊恩：詭影任務|傑克萊恩：詭影任務]]》（2014年，另一部克蘭西電影）的導師威廉·哈柏（{{lang|en|William Harper}}）一角；但該版本最後被認為已作廢。<ref>{{cite web |title=Is Tom Hardy Without Remorse? |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2012/08/21/is-tom-hardy-without-remorse |website=IGN |access-date=2018-09-22 |archive-date=2021-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304000248/https://www.ign.com/articles/2012/08/21/is-tom-hardy-without-remorse |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2017年，據報導，[[阿奇瓦·高斯曼|阿奇瓦·高斯曼]]與同家公司簽約，製作另一部由克拉克主演的電影改編《[[彩虹六号_(小说)|彩虹六號]]》<ref>{{cite web |last1=Fleming Jr. |first1=Mike |title=Akiva Goldsman To Paramount; 'Rainbow Six', 'Ologies' & 'Avengelyne' |url=https://deadline.com/2017/07/akiva-goldsman-tom-clancy-rainbow-six-ologies-avengelyne-paramount-1202126928/ |website=Deadline |date=2017-07-11 |access-date=2018-12-06 |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309030532/https://deadline.com/2017/07/akiva-goldsman-tom-clancy-rainbow-six-ologies-avengelyne-paramount-1202126928/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年9月20日，[[麥可·B·喬丹|麥可·B·喬丹]]將在兩部電影《冷血悍將》《彩虹六號》中飾演克拉克，電影由高斯曼、喬丹、{{le|喬希·阿貝爾鮑姆|Josh Appelbaum}}和{{le|安德烈·納梅克|André Nemec}}監製<ref>{{cite web |last1=Kroll |first1=Justin |title=Michael B. Jordan to Play Tom Clancy Character John Clark |url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/michael-b-jordan-john-clark-tom-clancy-movies-1202896241/ |website=Variety |date=2018-09-20 |access-date=2018-12-06 |archive-date=2021-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314125231/https://variety.com/2018/film/news/michael-b-jordan-john-clark-tom-clancy-movies-1202896241/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年12月，[[斯特法諾·索利瑪|斯特法諾·索利瑪]]受雇擔任導演<ref>{{cite news |last1=Kroll |first1=Justin |title=‘Sicario 2’ Filmmaker to Direct Michael B. Jordan in ‘Without Remorse’ Adaptation (EXCLUSIVE) |url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/sicario-2-without-remorse-michael-b-jordan-1203081476/ |access-date=2018-12-06 |work=Variety |date=2018-12-05 |archive-date=2021-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314125310/https://variety.com/2018/film/news/sicario-2-without-remorse-michael-b-jordan-1203081476/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年1月9日，《綜藝》宣布[[泰勒·謝里丹|泰勒·謝里丹]]將重寫劇本；謝里丹和索利瑪先前曾在《[[怒火邊界2：毒刑者|怒火邊界2：毒刑者]]》（2018年）中合作過。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Kroll |first1=Justin |title=Taylor Sheridan to Rewrite Michael B. Jordan’s ‘Without Remorse’ (EXCLUSIVE) |url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/taylor-sheridan-michael-b-jordan-without-remorse-120310