== 發行 ==
《湯姆·克蘭西之冷血悍將》定於2021年4月30日上線[[亞馬遜影片|亞馬遜影片]]平台<ref name="releasethr">{{cite news |last1=Kit |first1=Borys |title=Michael B. Jordan's Outlier Society Signs Film Deal With Amazon |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/michael-b-jordan-outlier-society-sign-film-deal-with-amazon |access-date=2021-02-08 |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2021-02-08 |archive-date=2021-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209103100/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/michael-b-jordan-outlier-society-sign-film-deal-with-amazon |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影原定於2020年9月18日由[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙影業]]在美國院線上映<ref>{{cite news |last1=Couch |first1=Aaron |title=Michael B. Jordan's 'Without Remorse' Sets 2020 Release Date |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/remorse-movie-release-date-set-2020-1182499 |access-date=2019-04-06 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2019-02-04 |archive-date=2020-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216155637/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/remorse-movie-release-date-set-2020-1182499 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但受[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]疫情影響而改為2020年10月2日<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/michael-b-jordans-remorse-snaps-up-new-2020-release-date-1291356|title=Michael B. Jordan's 'Without Remorse' Snaps Up New Fall 2020 Release Date|website=The Hollywood Reporter|language=en|access-date=2020-04-22|archive-date=2020-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200702025109/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/michael-b-jordans-remorse-snaps-up-new-2020-release-date-1291356|dead-url=no}}</ref>，再延期至2021年2月26日<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/06/paramount-moves-without-remorse-to-2021-1202971473/|title=Paramount Moves ‘Without Remorse’ To 2021|date=2020-06-26|access-date=2020-06-26|archive-date=2020-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200626230631/https://deadline.com/2020/06/paramount-moves-without-remorse-to-2021-1202971473/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年7月，{{le|亞馬遜影業|Amazon Studios}}與派拉蒙交易以獲取電影的發行權，排定上線亞馬遜影片<ref name="Amazon">{{cite web|url=https://www.variety.com/2020/film/news/michael-b-jordan-without-remorse-amazon-1234714715/|title=Amazon Nears Deal for Michael B. Jordan’s ‘Without Remorse’ (EXCLUSIVE)|website=Variety|first=Brent|last=Lang|date=2020-07-23|access-date=2020-09-23|archive-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231004147/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/michael-b-jordan-without-remorse-amazon-1234714715/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。派拉蒙2020年11月將電影從院線檔期上正式撤下<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/paramount-pictures-takes-michael-b-jordan-pic-without-remorse-micronauts-off-2021-release-calendar|title=Paramount Pictures Takes Michael B. Jordan Pic 'Without Remorse,' 'Micronauts' Off 2021 Release Calendar|date=2020-11-13|access-date=2021-01-21|author=Trilby Beresford|work=[[Hollywood_Reporter|Hollywood Reporter]]|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114231526/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/paramount-pictures-takes-michael-b-jordan-pic-without-remorse-micronauts-off-2021-release-calendar|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[第五十五届超级碗|第五十五届超级碗]]上，電影的麥可·B·喬丹隨[[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜公司]]的[[Amazon_Alexa|Alexa]]商業廣告中亮相<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://screencrush.com/michael-b-jordan-super-bowl-ad/|title=Michael B. Jordan’s Becomes Alexa in Amazon’s Super Bowl Ad|website=ScreenCrush|accessdate=2021-03-14|archive-date=2021-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314125233/https://screencrush.com/michael-b-jordan-super-bowl-ad/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

